The trustee for Petters Group
Worldwide LLC sued JPMorgan Chase & Co. in federal court in
Minnesota over claims the bank, along with other defendants,
received more than $300 million from a Ponzi scheme run by
Thomas J. Petters.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Michael Hytha at 
 mhytha@bloomberg.net  